    <div class="cns-content index-product-content">
      <i class="fa product-card-letter" aria-hidden="true"><span>R</span></i>
      <a href="#">
        Pea Gravel
      </a>
      <p class="card-text">pea gravel is known for it's attractive appearance and is commonly used in above
        ground
        applications. These types of projects can include walkways and areas around stepping stones in
        walkways.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="offering item portfolio-item">
    <div class="cns-img">
      <%= image_tag("drain-rock-10.jpg", alt: "10mm Drain Rock", class: "card-image-portfolio") %>
    </div>
    <div class="cns-content index-product-content">
      <i class="fa product-card-letter" aria-hidden="true"><span>R</span></i>
      <a href="#">
        10mm Drain Rock
      </a>
      <p class="card-text">Drainage gravels are generally used to help move water around, or away from, your
        property. The most common usage is behind retaining walls or drainage trenches underneath lawns and
        gardens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="offering item portfolio-item">
    <div class="cns-img">
      <%= image_tag("drain-rock-20.jpg", alt: "20mm Drain Rock", class: "card-image-portfolio") %>
    </div>
    <div class="cns-content index-product-content">
      <i class="fa product-card-letter" aria-hidden="true"><span>R</span></i>
      <a href="#">
        20mm Drain Rock
      </a>
      <p class="card-text">Drainage gravels are generally used to help move water around, or away from, your
        property. The most common usage is behind retaining walls or drainage trenches underneath lawns and
        gardens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="offering item portfolio-item">
    <div class="cns-img">
      <%= image_tag("oversized-rock.jpg", alt: "Oversized Rocks", class: "card-image-portfolio") %>
